reviewText: I disagree with the viewer who wrote that Jane and I are morons, but do agree with him that, at least for most people interested in investing, this is 8 hours worth watching (I found the investors we interviewed fascinating) but not ordinarily worth spending a hundred bucks to own.

As a financial professional, those videos are big disappointment to me. It didn't offer any insightful ideas, but instead that contents offered in the videos are comment knowledge in term finance. I wouldnt recommend this video to anyone who has finance background.
